room_title: Escape room "Save the SS Godspeed" by Room Escape Williamsburg in Williamsburg
room_description: You and fellow explorers are on a journey to settle a new planet, in route your ship gets damaged by an asteroid. When you wake up you find the ship's crew has abandoned ship, you have 60 minutes to restart the ship's engines before hurtling into a nearby star. Can you save the ship and continue your mission or will you be incinerated?
